				\begin{document}$${\tau }_{e}=\frac{1}{{\omega }_{max}}=\frac{1}{{2\pi f}_{max}}$$\end{document}

The cell with ZnO nanoflower as the photoanode material exhibits a higher τe\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
